title: Can't remember the name of this font!
content:
Found this font when looking for something that would look good for a decking company. The image shows 2 different styles of the same font family.  
Originally came across "Black Ops One" font which is similar and then found this which I liked better. I was even able to download a pdf with all the different versions of this font which I can't find anymore. I seem to remember the font name had something to do with a brand name, maybe automotive related? Any help is appreciated.  
Thanks.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317182839im_/http:/typophile.com/files/font_6209.jpg)
